ActWestern Economic Diversification Act
SubjectCanada Business Service Centre - Manitoba federal - provincial Agreement
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Western Economic Diversification to enter into a federal-provincial bilateral agreement to support the CANADA BUSINESS SERVICE CENTRE initiative in Manitoba. The agreement is for three years, terminating on March 31, 2014.
